Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.07,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何も怖くなんてないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.68,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手にしたものを失うくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:51.42,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}争いを待つ事を繰り返して
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.92,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}かすめて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何もかもを欲しがっていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迷えるものの誓い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:05.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}未だ見ぬ世界を創りだす事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.57,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}朽ち果てていく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:15.58,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}哀しい夢を遮るものは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.37,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自らの闇だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.93,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.26,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.43,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.60,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Makes me feel何処からか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.36,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}流れる景色変わらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.28,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}音もなく解き放つ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.10,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}畏れ断ち切り何時からか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.24,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}高鳴る鼓動止まらなくなって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.48,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}易しくも消し去って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:42.07,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我并非是在胆怯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.68,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去曾经的拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.68,0:00:51.42,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}等待着周而复始的纷争
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.92,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}掠夺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:56.18,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}曾经渴求着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.19,0:00:59.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}立下极易迷失的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:05.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必将创造出人们从未见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:08.57,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}直至此生的终结
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.73,0:01:15.58,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}阻挡哀伤之梦的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:19.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是自身的迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.93,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you make your time stand still
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.26,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You'll know what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.26,0:01:28.43,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But why would you want to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.55,0:01:31.60,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Makes me feel会有一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.76,0:01:35.36,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}变幻之景不再更迭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:38.28,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}悄然间将自身解放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:46.10,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}切断畏惧后不知从何开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:49.24,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}内心的悸动无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:52.48,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}却又轻易地将其熄灭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:16.62,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}向かい風吹く 一寸先 予想も出来ない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一心不乱 キミに付いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.75,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一期一会の宝を目指して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:29.07,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}足が震えても 止まらない 胸の高鳴り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.97,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}前人未到 旅はいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.00,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全身全霊 エンジン全開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:40.97,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絶対キミを守る どんなリスクがあるとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.58,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}‘絶対'なんかないさ チカラを尽くそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:55.09,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思い切り吸い込んだ 果てしない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Star the space-time trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.68,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}望遠鏡覗けば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.44,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}カリスマティックな闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}うねる波の迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(365,330)}ラビリンス
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:15.92,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Never stop! 幽閉された星を解き放つため
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}キミと旅立とう 月が明日へ導く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(375,330)}あす
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:16.62,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}迎风而立 未来无法预料
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:19.62,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一心一意 追随在你左右
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.62,0:22:22.75,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誓取一生的珍宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.89,0:22:29.07,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}即便脚步颤抖不已 也难阻心中的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.07,0:22:31.97,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}前无古人 随时启程
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.04,0:22:35.00,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全心全力 火力全开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:40.97,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}绝对要保护你 无论艰难险阻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.15,0:22:47.58,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凡事没有绝对 但会竭尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.59,0:22:55.09,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}彻底掉入无尽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Star the space-time trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.97,0:23:01.68,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}从望远镜中看去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:05.44,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充满诱惑的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.59,0:23:08.84,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}曲曲折折的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:15.92,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Never stop! 解放幽闭之星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.94,0:23:23.56,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}与你同行 月引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:06.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以来 人们就对妖怪心存畏惧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:12.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而走在那众妖之前 统领着百鬼夜行的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.98,0:00:16.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们称其为妖怪的总大将
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.18,0:00:18.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抑或是如此称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魑魅魍魉之主
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:23.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑头鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:04.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 怎么了 少主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:05.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 雪女
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.71,0:02:09.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 好美的月亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:11.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:16.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样平安地过着每一天真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:18.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去打架的好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.18,0:02:19.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:23.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:31.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆生决意包容造反的牛鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.78,0:02:41.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过陆生尚未察觉 在西方刮起了不安定的风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:47.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(130,300)}魔镜来袭 吞食果实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:03:00.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:05.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又做那个梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从6岁开始一直重复的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:24.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天明明是我的生日 却糟糕地醒来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.80,0:03:33.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:37.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那个奇怪的梦害我没睡好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:43.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 你才6岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.86,0:03:47.76,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么长大了再来一起玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.72,0:03:52.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了哦 我会来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:53.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:56.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:03:58.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:03.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:06.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岛同学真不愧是U-14日本代表
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:11.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你来帮忙 青田坊…不是 仓田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:13.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也谢谢冰丽前来加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:22.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 像这样 这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别觉得不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.17,0:04:26.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是可以保护自己不被妖怪伤害的愚歩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是面向超级初学者的版本哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.34,0:04:31.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们非要…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:34.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学这种东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:38.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这都为了你们好 还想全裸时被袭击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么约定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:49.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 家长同学也来学习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.71,0:04:50.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:54.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实应该最先学会的人是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:57.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很容易被妖怪盯上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 跟着做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.15,0:05:03.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 大家都在练习呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在做愚歩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:11.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝天白云下 修行阴阳护身术
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.02,0:05:15.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多美妙的青春之页啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:19.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 新的妖怪体验大会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:20.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:27.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家长同学 今天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:29.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:32.66,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:38.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一家人 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛快快地收下礼物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:42.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:45.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么 里面有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:48.18,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这盒子好像是名牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:54.96,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅…诅咒人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:56.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是把家长同学妖怪化的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:03.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 超可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:07.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 这可是特别订做的高级商品呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.65,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么无聊的想法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:11.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你了 清继同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.67,0:06:13.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我今天先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 不参加发表会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.75,0:06:18.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我有点睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩把这个搬回教室了 你们可以先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:26.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:29.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要先准备晚饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.47,0:06:32.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:35.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 少主就交给我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.09,0:06:39.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那我先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:41.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以回来得太晚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.84,0:06:42.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早点回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:54.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然能收到生日礼物很高兴 不过这实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.36,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:02.72,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在你生日那天来接你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.35,0:07:05.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.53,0:07:11.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们听说过紫之镜的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:12.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫之镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.90,0:07:15.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 妖怪云外镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.81,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通称紫之镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:20.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也叫照魔镜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:25.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看一眼这个镜子就会被诅咒 并且在13岁生日那天被杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车站有这么远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:35.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.32,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是13岁？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:42.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自古以来 在妖怪的世界里13岁是成人年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:44.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:47.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说成人了就会被杀掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 因为已经成熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:53.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人又不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.17,0:07:54.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 奴良同学 你来晚了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在打扫教室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:01.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 加奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你13岁生日快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:28.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 我来接你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:34.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈来一起玩吧 继续7年前的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.33,0:08:39.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊 从梦里出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:40.90,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩躲猫猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:48.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 愚歩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:01.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:02.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:08.17,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校？怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在镜子里玩躲猫猫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:24.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我明明是往车站走的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:27.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为什么会到学校了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:41.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫色的镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:48.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 你才6岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:51.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么长大了再来一起玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:56.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约好了哦 我会来接你的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:01.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你13岁生日那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那时的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:09.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 这个房间没有镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:10.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狭窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狭窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:14.70,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,云外镜？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.45,0:10:17.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:22.31,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然没听说过 但应该是被哪个组开除的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:26.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 今天是加奈的生日呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:30.25,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 对 关于刚才的生日礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我还准备了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:33.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.22,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:37.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是把我妖怪化的可爱的人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:39.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.21,0:10:42.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出不来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:50.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜…镜子 又要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:52.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:59.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 到底怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:04.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清继同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:13.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃惊了吧 其实这人偶里装了移动电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.99,0:11:16.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是清十字团的通信器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:26.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊 现在我被怪物 从镜子里出来的怪物袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:27.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家长同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:29.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:30.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.16,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈 现在你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:35.94,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校的某个男厕所里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:39.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家长同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:58.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个男厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:04.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清继同学你们找那边 我找这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.58,0:12:08.50,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.19,0:12:12.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.26,0:12:14.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清继同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:15.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.45,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看不见我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.23,0:12:25.71,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有人来哦 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:32.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆…陆生同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:37.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能看到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.63,0:12:41.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只属?我和加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:46.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:52.62,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:55.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 被吸走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:57.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.79,0:13:07.57,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:12.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混球 别在我的地盘上对女人动手动脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:15.38,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 你是妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:19.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别来…别来妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:29.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 不知道哪个才是真身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.67,0:13:30.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然不知道 那全砍了就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢…谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:01.69,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家长同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.45,0:14:05.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.55,0:14:06.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不在这边 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.64,0:14:08.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪儿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:12.09,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家长同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:12.93,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.55,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.04,0:14:21.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点睡眠不足 在迷糊时看到了这个人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:23.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.05,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.37,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:40.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被老鼠妖怪抓住的时候 合宿的时候 现在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次只要有陆生同学在 你就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.35,0:14:46.88,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:52.84,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.06,0:14:57.27,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你 再多陪我一会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.27,0:15:01.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再告诉我一些你的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:06.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算留下可怕的回忆也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:22.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.62,0:15:26.75,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 害怕了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.06,0:15:33.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 和你在一起 什么都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.77,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:43.80,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很想知道我的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:53.06,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会完全告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:12.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.62,0:16:15.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.81,0:16:20.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到妖怪和风餐馆化猫屋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.81,0:16:22.33,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.34,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺象样的嘛 干得不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.99,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我好了 我已不会再出错了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:37.67,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说少主 这女孩不是被旧鼠抓走的人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.41,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带她来这种地方真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:45.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 良太猫 交给你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:49.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:52.46,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不能小看少主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.49,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟带来了位这么可爱的情人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:56.04,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家都吃醋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:02.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说他被称作少主 看来这个人真的是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:05.10,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:08.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:09.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少岁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,12…不 今天就13岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:16.87,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是生日？那真是恭喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:21.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说今天就成人了 真是太可喜可贺了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.73,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成为一个出色的妖怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 你是什么妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:27.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:31.43,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他们知道你是人类 一会儿会吃掉你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:34.03,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.17,0:17:37.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 呐 到底是什么妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:38.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:42.59,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 我要被吃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.13,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜…镜子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:48.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是你的生日吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:52.52,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.28,0:17:54.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人偶好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:05.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪儿买的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.85,0:18:06.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:07.19,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:08.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪的世界原来是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:15.47,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟想象的有点不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:22.26,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱啊 这孩子也是妖怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.51,0:18:24.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.32,0:18:25.40,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…少主
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:29.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有各种妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:35.63,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃饱喝足了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:39.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜品店婆婆的料理水平真高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.78,0:18:47.58,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主真是的 都这个时候了还不回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:53.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么「少主就交给我好了」 竟然把少主跟丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:55.11,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.17,0:18:57.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:04.64,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫先生 木天蓼果汁真好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.79,0:19:09.15,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 能玩得尽兴真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:13.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙招待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:26.89,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 陆生是早上才回来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.07,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.42,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这小子真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:36.35,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这孩子很行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:41.51,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说我在做什么啊 怎么做出了昨天那种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:46.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 少主 昨天晚上你去哪里做了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.49,0:19:48.68,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:49.85,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.56,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加…加奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.54,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上抱歉了…啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:54.21,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:59.44,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 陆生同学 我有点事想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:02.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.53,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么晚上？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.78,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要问什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:15.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想了想之前到现在的行动 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.55,0:20:17.82,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有陆生同学那个人就会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.26,0:20:25.08,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道陆生同学和那个人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 要穿帮了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.20,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.23,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 告诉我关于那个人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:40.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽…虽然我不是很明白 为什么想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:46.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不行的啊 跟陆生同学又没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.86,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 还没开始营业
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:10.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.14,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大的声音啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:15.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三郎猫 你的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.79,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才突然刮起的风弄的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.32,0:21:23.29,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 只不过衣服破了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:24.39,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.24,0:21:26.02,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:35.74,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是衣服坏了？他还真是什么都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:40.48,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来奴良组的幼稚是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.01,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来侦察真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:45.97,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴良组的根据地浮世绘町
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:50.28,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镇压这个街道所需要的时间…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.97,0:21:52.61,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多一星期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:30.92,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个领子好紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.12,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呢 阿青
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:34.30,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领子上的扣子不是都解开的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.39,0:23:35.60,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个季节你还围围巾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:36.83,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:38.95,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 滑头鬼之孙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.18,0:23:40.98,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西风打头阵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Chinese,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
